OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,FSeveral strikes were in busy
OL,7,Fcommercial locations, causing panic in
OL,8,Fthe streets.
OL,10,FAt the time of writing, Lebanon's
OL,11,Fhealth ministry said dozens of people
OL,12,Fhave been killed and hundreds more
OL,13,Fwounded.
OL,15,FIt comes after US President Donald
OL,16,FTrump announced he had agreed to a two-
OL,17,Fweek ceasefire with Tehran, which
OL,18,Fwould see a pause in military strikes
OL,19,Fagainst Iran and a reopening of the
OL,20,Fvital Strait of Hormuz strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,FIsrael has said it has agreed to the
OL,7,Fceasefire but that it does not apply
OL,8,Fto its conflict with Hezbollah in
OL,9,FLebanon.
OL,11,FOther nations, including Pakistan,
OL,12,Fwhich helped with negotiations, have
OL,13,Fclaimed the deal does include Lebanon.
OL,15,FLebanon's Minister of Social Affairs
OL,16,FHaneed Sayed condemned Israel's wide
OL,17,Frange of strikes, calling it a "very
OL,18,Fdangerous turning point" in the
OL,19,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,F"These hits are now at the heart of
OL,7,FBeirut ... Half of the sheltered
OL,8,F(internally displaced persons) are in
OL,9,FBeirut in this area," she said.
OL,11,FShe also said Lebanon's government is
OL,12,Fready to enter into negotiations with
OL,13,FIsrael for an end to hostilities, an
OL,14,Foffer the president previously made.
OL,15,FIsrael has not responded.
OL,17,F"There are calls and efforts being
OL,18,Fmade as we speak," Sayed said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,FLebanon's Prime Minister Nawaf Salam
OL,7,Faccused Israel of escalating at a
OL,8,Fmoment when Lebanese officials were
OL,9,Fseeking to negotiate a solution, and
OL,10,Fof hitting civilian areas in "utter
OL,11,Fdisregard for the principles of
OL,12,Finternational law and international
OL,13,Fhumanitarian law - principles it has,
OL,14,Fin any case, never respected."
OL,16,FIsrael's military said it had targeted
OL,17,Fmissile launchers, command centers and
OL,18,Fintelligence infrastructure and
OL,19,Faccused Hezbollah of using civilians
OL,20,Fas human shields.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
