OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,F"The State of Lebanon and its
OL,7,Fcivilians must refuse Hezbollah's
OL,8,Fentrenchment in civilian areas and its
OL,9,Fweapons build-up capabilities," the
OL,10,FIDF said in a statement.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
