PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775758264
OL,3,CIsrael launches 'largest' strikes on
OL,4,CLebanon yet amid ceasefire uncertainty
OL,6,FBefore the wave of new strikes, a
OL,7,FHezbollah official told the Associated
OL,8,FPress that the group was giving a
OL,9,Fchance for mediators to secure a
OL,10,Fceasefire in Lebanon, but "we have not
OL,11,Fannounced our adherence to the
OL,12,Fceasefire since the Israelis are not
OL,13,Fadhering to it."
OL,15,FHe spoke on condition of anonymity
OL,16,Fbecause he was not authorised to
OL,17,Fcomment publicly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
